03:51.840 --> 03:55.160
Yeah. Buster Brady, that fecker? Yes!

03:55.160 --> 03:57.320
I thought you might
have picked Mark.

03:57.320 --> 04:00.200
I'd love to see my
two sons on the altar.

04:00.200 --> 04:03.040
Well, I wasn't best man at his
wedding. You were in prison, love.

04:04.760 --> 04:07.000
Still...I'd like Buster.

04:07.000 --> 04:08.520
Well, think about Mark.

04:13.640 --> 04:15.680
Tell me this.

04:15.680 --> 04:19.040
