27:41.320 --> 27:42.840
Go on.

27:50.280 --> 27:51.320
Agnes.

27:55.720 --> 27:57.920
Jesus Christ, Winnie.

27:57.920 --> 28:03.400
You know you were saying about us
two marrying our best friends? Yes?

28:03.400 --> 28:06.840
Well, I didn't marry my best friend.

28:06.840 --> 28:09.800
I moved in beside her.

28:15.080 --> 28:16.640
I wonder who that fecking was.

28:20.560 --> 28:22.280
Goodnight, friends.

